          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Some background: In this age of corporate-owned media, we are trying to find new ways to make grassroots-funded media more accessible and affordable to the widest possible audience — and so we’re trying out this kind of partnership that offers our subscribers an exclusive discount.",
            "type": "text",
