      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Scroll down and you’ll see we’ve attached an excerpt of one of Discourse Blog’s recent pieces so you can get a sense of what they do. They are writers who used to write for the now-defunct website Splinter — and as I said, I’m a big fan. You can also check out their offerings at ",
